snippet.title: Football Manager 25 | The New Era | #FM25 Official Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
Welcome to the new era of football management. FM25 out from 26th Nov. 

Feed your obsession for the beautiful game with Football Manager 25. 

• FM25 on PC/Mac
• FM25 Console on Xbox, Xbox Game Pass and PlayStation 5
• FM25 Mobile exclusively on Netflix Games
• FM25 Touch on Nintendo Switch

Pre-purchase FM25 before 26th Nov for 10% off on PC/Mac from participating digital retailers.

Pre-purchase here 👉 https://fm25.store/Pre-Purchase

Discover our FM25 Roadmap and more detail 👉 https://fm25.info/Roadmap

Join our FMFC squad to take advantage of early and exclusive news, competitions and insights across the season 👉 https://FMFC.info/SignUp
